dealerListings.description: MInt mint mint is the best way to describe this boat.   We have never seen a used boat this clean even if it was 1 yr old.   Repowered with an economical 90hp Evinrude HO motor in 2016 she is ready to go.  Large Garmin display sounder/chartplotter, Garmin VHF.  If you see this boat she will not disapoint.  The Montauk has been a worldwide favorite for decades, thanks to its center console design, superior lateral stability, its extra-dry ride and quick planing with minimal horsepower. Today’s Boston Whaler 170 Montauk carries on the tradition and raises the bar. Enjoy a soft ride and smooth performance, provided by its modified V-hull entry. With a wide 6' 10" beam, there’s ample room inside for people and gear, while you still get quick planing, great performance and a shallow, 9-inch draft. The center console puts everything at your fingertips, and there’s a spacious storage / anchor locker in the bow.
